---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Us | fashionCulture">
    <main>
        <section class="about-section">
            <h1>About Us</h1>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Welcome to fashionCulture</h2>
                <p>
                    At fashionCulture, we believe that fashion is more than just clothingâ€”it's an expression of who you are. Our brand is built on the foundation of timeless elegance, modern sophistication, and an unwavering commitment to quality. We are passionate about curating a collection that speaks to the diverse tastes and styles of our customers, ensuring that everyone can find something that resonates with their unique identity.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
                <p>
                    Inspired by the sophistication of brands like Massimo Dutti and the personalized approach of About You, fashionCulture aims to bring you an unparalleled shopping experience. We understand that fashion is deeply personal, and we strive to offer a collection that reflects the varied lifestyles of our customers. Whether you're looking for something casual, chic, or classic, our curated selections are designed to cater to every occasion.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Our Collections</h2>
                <p>
                    Each piece in our collection is carefully selected with a focus on quality craftsmanship, premium materials, and contemporary designs. We collaborate with some of the finest designers and artisans around the world to bring you clothing that not only looks good but feels exceptional. From luxurious fabrics to intricate details, our garments are made to stand the test of time, offering both style and substance.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Sustainability and Responsibility</h2>
                <p>
                    At fashionCulture, we are committed to responsible fashion. We recognize the impact of the fashion industry on the environment, and we are taking steps to reduce our carbon footprint. Our sustainable practices include sourcing eco-friendly materials, partnering with ethical suppliers, and promoting slow fashion. We believe in creating fashion that not only looks good but also does good for the planet.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Customer-Centric Experience</h2>
                <p>
                    We put our customers at the heart of everything we do. Inspired by the customer-first philosophy of brands like About You, fashionCulture offers a personalized shopping experience tailored to your needs. Our online platform is designed to be intuitive and user-friendly, allowing you to explore our collections with ease. Our dedicated customer service team is always here to assist you, ensuring that your shopping experience is as seamless and enjoyable as possible.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Join the fashionCulture Community</h2>
                <p>
                    Fashion is a journey, and we invite you to embark on it with us. Join the fashionCulture community and stay connected with the latest trends, exclusive offers, and behind-the-scenes insights. Follow us on social media, subscribe to our newsletter, and become a part of a growing community that celebrates fashion in all its forms.
                </p>
                <p>Thank you for choosing fashionCulture. We look forward to being a part of your fashion journey.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <style>
        main {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .about-section {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #444;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .content-block p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content-block {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</Layout>
